Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:29.09,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吸進不可置信的深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:32.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目に見えるものだけの世界現象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:32.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這滿溢只為肉眼所見事物的世界現象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:34.77,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴き出せるか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:34.77,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否將其揭露
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plastic　Plastic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plastic　Plastic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:40.44,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ　誰もおかしくなれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:40.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 誰也不會變得奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.44,0:01:43.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴様もPlastic in for World
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.44,0:01:43.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也只不過是Plastic in for World
